InteGrade (Version 0.2) - Mon Nov 21 16:59:33 BRST 2005

* Name server (NFS is not required anymore)

* Security in Application Repository

* Improvements in asctGui

* Some bugs fixed and documentation updated

* Simplifications in installation procedures

----------------------------------------------------------------------

InteGrade (Version 0.1) - Fri Feb  4 14:52:38 BRST 2005

* This is the first InteGrade release!

* Support for BSMP communication in BSPlib.

* Documentation Updated.

* Improvements in InteGrade's BSPlib

